Class AccessibleTableCellEvent

java.lang.Object
  SWTEventObject
      org.eclipse.swt.accessibility.AccessibleTableCellEvent

public class AccessibleTableCellEvent
extends SWTEventObject

Instances of this class are sent as a result of accessibility clients sending AccessibleTableCell messages to an accessible object.

Since:
1.4
See Also:
AccessibleTableCellListener, AccessibleTableCellAdapter
